dcterms:creator: F. Mo
dcterms:description: A chiral molecular retention time dataset (CMRT dataset) established by collecting experimental data reported in 644 articles about asymmetric catalysis. The dataset contains the retention time of 25,847 molecules, including 11,720 pairs of enantiomers, along with experimental information and HPLC column information. The molecules are recorded in the form of SMILES.
dcterms:title: Chiral Molecular Retention Time Dataset (CMRT dataset)
